      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先搭建基础结构：main分支上创建第一个commit，然后branch出develop，checkout到develop再做第二个commit。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit",
        "branch develop",
